message.content:
Here is a healthy meal plan for you that doesn't contain any of the ingredients you mentioned:

Monday:
- Breakfast: Overnight oats with berries, chia seeds, and almond milk
- Lunch: Quinoa and black bean salad with avocado, cherry tomatoes, cucumber, and balsamic vinaigrette
- Dinner: Lentil and vegetable curry with brown rice

Wednesday:
- Breakfast: Greek yogurt with honey, fresh berries, and a drizzle of maple syrup
- Lunch: Roasted root vegetables with garlic and lemon
- Dinner: Stuffed bell peppers with quinoa, black beans, and avocado

Friday:
- Breakfast: Smoothie bowl with spinach, kale, almond milk, and a scoop of protein powder
- Lunch: Chickpea salad with cherry tomatoes, cucumber, and a drizzle of olive oil
- Dinner: Spaghetti squash with turkey meatballs and a side salad

Remember to drink plenty of water and eat a balanced diet to keep your health and well-being in check..
